From: Andrew Morton <akpm@linux-foundation.org>
Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:12:32 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] 
 mm-vmalloc-acquire-init_mm-lock-on-huge-vmap-to-avoid-ptdump-uaf-fix

update comment, per Kiryl

